(5892, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done! I\'ll put these supplies to good use! Thanks, $N!', 12340),
(5893, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ah, you got them. Good work, $N! These supplies are a little musty from sitting in that dark mine for so long, but we\'ll make use of them nonetheless.$B$BThank you, $N. Your deeds are vital to the maintenance of our fighting forces.', 12340),
(5901, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'These will do nicely, $N. Thank you.$B$BIf you\'re ready, we can get on with the next step.', 12340),
(5903, 1, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'These will do nicely, $N. Thank you. Just look at them... so many of them all huddled up. I almost feel bad for the Crusade, but then again, it was never their mill to take, now, was it?', 12340),
(5923, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am glad you found your way here today. young $c. The time has come for you to take a large step into a much larger world.$B$BInside each of Cenarius\' children is the call to serve nature. Animals and plants are our friends as well as our charges. We choose to devote our lives as preservers of balance for their sakes as well as our own. Your first step into this world will be to learn of the ways of the bear, and to learn strength of body and heart.$B$BReady yourself!', 12340),
(5924, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am glad you found your way here today. young $c. The time has come for you to take a large step into a much larger world.$B$BInside each of Cenarius\' children is the call to serve nature. Animals and plants are our friends as well as our charges. We choose to devote our lives as preservers of balance for their sakes as well as our own. Your first step into this world will be to learn of the ways of the bear, and to learn strength of body and heart.$B$BReady yourself!', 12340),
