(7839, 1, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My tools! You found them! Oh glorious day! Thank you, $N.', 12340),
(7843, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I wish I coulda been there to see the look on their faces, mon. Are they packing up their bags? Leavin\' town?$B$BYou done good, $N. Real good. Otho reward you with the big mojo.', 12340),
(7844, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done, $c. Zul\'jin himself could not have done a better job!', 12340),
(7845, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You must act quickly, $N. Surely the guards have been alerted to your presence.', 12340),
(7846, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Freedom at last! Thank you, $N. Revantusk will know your deeds!', 12340),
(7847, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have done the Revantusk a great service, $N! We owe you a great debt of gratitude.', 12340),
(7849, 1, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My dearest brother, how I will miss you...$B$BThank you for your assistance, $N. You are truly a hero in my eyes.', 12340),
(7861, 21, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A crippling blow to the Vilebranch, indeed. You shall be richly rewarded, $N.', 12340),
(7862, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You are indeed a worthy candidate for the new position, $N. Accept this trinket as a token of our appreciation for your hard work. I will be reviewing all applications next year.', 12340),
(7863, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Warsong Gulch. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Gulch, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Friendly with us, and bandages when you are Honored.', 12340),
