(8635, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The battles of ages past are seeds from which legends grow. Yours is a time of heroes, young one. May your legend take root, thrive.$B$BI bid you well, $N, and offer you this token...', 12340),
(8636, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The stuff of life is doomed to die and return to the earth, but the stuff of spirit lives eternal. I bid you well, $N, and offer you this token...', 12340),
